dct_title_s: Carte des chemins de fer, des chaussées et des voies navigables de L'Empire de Russie =
dct_alternative_sm: карта железныхъ, шоссейныхъ и внутреннихъ водныхъ, путей сообщения Российской империи
dct_description_sm: Cyrillic transcribed into latin script by cataloger.
Cartouche (glued over original Cyrillic) and panel in French, map in Russian (Cyrillic).
Color legend: "rajon vod, podvedomstvennyh mvu putej soobŝenija."
Shows railways, waterways, various roads and routes.
